EXERCISE 16 - mailregisterapp | HOL 16: Form Validation
============================================================
Category  : Mandatory
Topic     : Form validation, controlled components, error display
App Name  : mailregisterapp
Status    : COMPLETED ✅

------------------------------------------------------------
VALIDATION RULES
------------------------------------------------------------
  ✔ Name    : length >= 5 characters
  ✔ Email   : must contain @ AND .
  ✔ Password: length >= 8 characters

------------------------------------------------------------
VALIDATION METHOD
------------------------------------------------------------
  validate(name, value) {
    case 'name':     return value.length < 5 ? 'Error...' : ''
    case 'email':    return (!includes('@') || !includes('.')) ? ...
    case 'password': return value.length < 8 ? 'Error...' : ''
  }

  handleChange() → validates on every keystroke (real-time)
  handleSubmit() → validates all before submit

